              "Step 3 — Assign occurrence scores (1–5): evaluate how likely the attribute is to vary outside the desired range during manufacturing. Consider process sensitivity (DoE data), stability trends (forced degradation), and platform history. High-occurrence attributes include deamidation at labile Asn-Gly sites and Met oxidation.",
